<英文法規名稱>Regulations Governing the Operational Procedures and Compensation for Expropriation of Manufacturing Equipment and Raw Materials of Disease Prevention Supplies for Severe Pneumonia with Novel Pathogens</英文法規名稱>
<中文法規名稱>嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎防疫物資之生產設備與原物料徵用調用作業程序及補償辦法</中文法規名稱>
